TableView.name: SELECTION_BOARD_CURRENT_VOTE
TableView.userDefinedSQL: SELECT SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE.* FROM SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE, ( SELECT BOARD_ID, NWA_ID, VOTER_ID, MAX(VOTE_ORDER) AS CURRENT_MAX_VOTE_ORDER FROM SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE GROUP BY BOARD_ID, NWA_ID, VOTER_ID ) SELECTION_BOARD_MAX_VOTE_ORDER WHERE SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE.BOARD_ID = SELECTION_BOARD_MAX_VOTE_ORDER.BOARD_ID AND SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE.NWA_ID = SELECTION_BOARD_MAX_VOTE_ORDER.NWA_ID AND SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE.VOTER_ID = SELECTION_BOARD_MAX_VOTE_ORDER.VOTER_ID AND SELECTION_BOARD_VOTE.VOTE_ORDER = SELECTION_BOARD_MAX_VOTE_ORDER.CURRENT_MAX_VOTE_ORDER
